Text: Email down for awhilethat many of you care But since I am moving to Tulsa my computer will be down for awhile and my email is going to be shut off this Friday Therefore I am going to have to move over to my hotmail account The address is However because of the limited space on hotmail I will have to ask you not to send large forwards for awhile I will write everybody when I get a new ISP and tell you guys the new address Scot Lilly
